{"tid":306974,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"拍拖拍到愈嚟愈大嘅無力感⋯","createTime":"2017-07-03T03:44:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-04T04:28:19.000Z","uid":43172,"like":13,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f1d84ea6297540aa65535971208d0d9b446678ec","tid":306974,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:44:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 借朋友ac 唔想比男朋友見到<br />\n<br />\n拍拖愈耐 愈辛苦 大家差距太大<br />\n佢屋企安安穩穩 我屋企好窮<br />\n好多時佢都唔明白我屋企嘅處境⋯<br />\n我對佢愈毫無保留 佢習保護膜好似愈嚟愈厚咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時我做錯小小野 佢都會嬲到我死⋯點氹都氹唔到 msg唔覆 但又唔知同邊個傾計 <br />\n有時我問佢小小野 係因為我知道咗啲關於佢嘅野 心裡諗唔明白先去問去<br />\n唔通我由得我一個去亂諗就叫好咩？<br />\n佢每次都話我發細路仔脾氣 話我幼稚 話我唔成熟<br />\n但佢無諗過自己有問題我先問 我淨係想問下 我淨係想知道佢點解會咁做<br />\n佢唔會諗我點解會咁做而直接係覺得我想撩交嗌而咁做<br />\n<br />\n心好累 點解會咁⋯<br />\n拍得愈耐 大家愈多唔好嘅野會現形<br />\n我知道我都有缺點 我為咗你會改⋯<br />\n以前我俾人寵壞哂 一嗌交我就玩失蹤 完全唔理你<br />\n依家我唔會再咁 有咩事大家心平氣和咁傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  我唔會再對你有任何保留同隱瞞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我以前係好港女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但我為咗你改變 但反而你依家都變得愈嚟愈差⋯你唔願意為我改變⋯次次講完嘅你改兩日 之後又打完原形⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢覺得佢已經對我好好，但其實我想要嘅唔係物質<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想要嘅係心靈慰藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我想感受到你嘅愛咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  愛由物質係換唔到 我唔需要呢啲野 我淨係想你真心真意愛我 錫我 明唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我唔想拍拖淨係得sex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  因為我愛你所以我俾你 但依家我已經唔想再搞<br />\n平時我講乜野你都可以聯想到sex嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想同你淨係得sex<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n點解淨你依家變到淨係<br />\n我感受唔到你嘅愛呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n無力感愈嚟愈大<br />\n愈嚟愈想放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者分開對大家會好啲？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好辛苦<br />\n一陣要見到佢 我已經唔想見<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我到底點樣做先好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e6b46c169e64fcfe0cd010a29d988d3fb6364e3","tid":306974,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"救命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 愈諗愈辛苦"},{"pid":"74fbc794e6f46cfd16a1f3fd7ff15a0be947c72b","tid":306974,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:47:34.000Z","msg":"失控痛哭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46e7b4462de411d5e027294e4cb751c5fd5924f2","tid":306974,"uid":91875,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:48:46.000Z","msg":"飛啦呢D人<br />\n縱過隆果下你已經做錯左"},{"pid":"6506fb7a41740768e71ccb4e46ff920bcb8bdc78","tid":306974,"uid":1436,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:49:05.000Z","msg":"拍得咁唔開心就散啦"},{"pid":"a7a1eceb1ecf0ff9880620d840c66b875af764fb","tid":306974,"uid":15335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:49:46.000Z","msg":"分開對你好啲"},{"pid":"ffea37fd481c622763f8c39a2c6173b19d128604","tid":306974,"uid":28510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:52:05.000Z","msg":"分啦"},{"pid":"023f84136e1155eced3d7979d8a8ba67df3c1fd5","tid":306974,"uid":43172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-03T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛啦呢D人<br